reviewText:
My brother had me order this for his wife for Christmas - she loved it!
(Why does this have a min. word count?)
If you are a history buff, you will enjoy this.  Facinating. Very well done.  I plan of getting the rest.
Purchased this DVD box set mainly for the Newport Mansions and Adirondack Camps, but have enjoyed all of the episodes from this series.  Great value compaired to the home site for this series.
